Featured Projects

● Time Overflowed
  ✦ Free open-source chrome extension that automatically tracks time spent on each website domain and provides users with detailed
    daily and weekly usage statistics for enhanced productivity insights.
  ✦ Tools Used: HTML, CSS, Javascript, Chrome APIs, Manifest v3.

● Curly Brackets
  ✦ Full-stack learning platform that lets users track their progress across web development topics with secure auth, persistent lesson data, and badge-based milestones.
  ✦ Applies best practices for secure auth, robust database‑backed progress tracking, and a beautiful, mobile‑first UI that works smoothly across devices.
  ✦ Tools Used: Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind, Supabase, Framer Motion
  ✦ Links: https://curlybrackets.vercel.app/

● Weave (in progress)
  ✦ Compiles structured user input into role-optimized portfolio source code with dynamic template injection.
  ✦ Abstracts themes into reusable UI modules and programmatically hydrates them with user-specific data.
  ✦ Generates deployment-ready static assets with scalable component architecture for rapid customization.
  ✦ Links: https://github.com/satvik-Hecker/weave

